text: Gymnacranthera maliliensis is a species of plant in the family Myristicaceae. It is endemic to Sulawesi in Indonesia. ==References== * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Gymnacranthera maliliensis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
